1
00:00:00,420 --> 00:00:01,420
Found it!

2
00:00:02,880 --> 00:00:04,080
Just like last year...

3
00:00:04,670 --> 00:00:05,460
It's the same!

4
00:00:05,460 --> 00:00:06,460
The font.

5
00:00:07,880 --> 00:00:09,790
Are you happy with it?

6
00:00:12,630 --> 00:00:13,630
What's wrong?

7
00:00:14,630 --> 00:00:15,790
That's not it...

8
00:00:17,960 --> 00:00:18,630
What about the font, then?

9
00:00:18,830 --> 00:00:19,420
It's different, isn't it?

10
00:00:19,420 --> 00:00:19,830
Huh?

11
00:00:20,250 --> 00:00:21,920
No, just look.

12
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:23,630
Take a closer look.

13
00:00:25,000 --> 00:00:26,000
It's fine.

14
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,210
That's strange...

15
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:34,750
I'm the one who was cheated on.

16
00:00:35,000 --> 00:00:36,420
I'm so pathetic...

17
00:00:36,580 --> 00:00:37,790
I...

18
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:38,670
Reika-san?

19
00:00:38,670 --> 00:00:39,670
Enough.

20
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:43,130
I hate you with all my heart.

21
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:45,290
And that will never change.

22
00:00:45,330 --> 00:00:46,330
Yes.

23
00:00:46,580 --> 00:00:47,710
I understand.

24
00:00:48,000 --> 00:00:49,460
Go on, keep it up.

25
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,960
I will personally drag you down
into the abyss.

26
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:53,420
Mark my words.

27
00:00:54,250 --> 00:00:55,250
Yes.

28
00:01:01,670 --> 00:01:03,380
What am I going to do...

29
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,880
She's so cute.

30
00:01:12,880 --> 00:01:14,500
I'm not letting her get to me.
